# 1. Basic GitHub Hosted Runner Example

---

# Workflow

```yaml
name: Hosted Runner Example

on: push

jobs:
  demo:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest

    steps:
      - name: Checkout Repository
        uses: actions/checkout@v4

      - name: Display Message
        run: echo "Running on GitHub Hosted Runner"
```

---

# What Happens?

| Step | Action                   |
| ---- | ------------------------ |
| 1    | GitHub creates Ubuntu VM |
| 2    | Repository cloned        |
| 3    | Echo command executed    |
| 4    | VM removed               |

---

# Output

```text
Running on GitHub Hosted Runner
```

---

