# 11. Real-World CI/CD Example

---

# Scenario

Company wants:

* Build app
* Run tests
* Deploy app

using Ubuntu runner.

---

# Workflow

```yaml
name: CI/CD Pipeline

on:
  push:
    branches:
      - main

jobs:
  build-and-test:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest

    steps:
      - name: Checkout Code
        uses: actions/checkout@v4

      - name: Install Dependencies
        run: npm install

      - name: Run Tests
        run: npm test

      - name: Build Application
        run: npm run build

  deploy:
    needs: build-and-test

    runs-on: ubuntu-latest

    steps:
      - name: Deploy Application
        run: echo "Deploying to production"
```

---

# Workflow Flow

```text
Push Code
    ↓
Ubuntu Runner Created
    ↓
Build + Test
    ↓
Deploy Job Starts
    ↓
Runner Destroyed
```

---

