# 14. Common Mistakes

---

# Mistake 1 – Assuming Data Persists

Hosted runners are temporary.

Files disappear after workflow ends.

---

# Mistake 2 – Hardcoding OS Commands

Linux commands may fail on Windows runners.

---

# Mistake 3 – Installing Large Dependencies Repeatedly

Can slow workflows.

Use caching.

---

# Mistake 4 – Exposing Secrets

Never print secrets in logs.

